 web|title=Don't label me 'Mohajir'|url=http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/20715/dont-label-me-mohajir/|access-date=17 June 2015|work=tribune.com.pk|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617192944/http://blogs.tribune.com.pk/story/20715/dont-label-me-mohajir/|archive-date=17 June 2015|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title='Mohajir card' – all key parties contesting by-polls using it|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-4-313662-Mohajir-card-%E2%80%93-all-key-parties-contesting-by-polls-using-it|access-date=17 June 2015|date=20 April 2015|work=The News International, Pakistan|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617192006/http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-4-313662-Mohajir-card-%E2%80%93-all-key-parties-contesting-by-polls-using-it|archive-date=17 June 2015|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Mohajir question|url=http://www.dawn.com/news/1082152|access-date=17 June 2015|author=Dr Niaz Murtaza|date=23 January 2014|work=dawn.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617190829/http://www.dawn.com/news/1082152|archive-date=17 June 2015|url-status=live}}</ref> 該詞指的是來自[[印度|印度]]的穆斯林移民，他們大多定居在[[信德省|信德]]的城市地區，取代了當地的[[信德人|信德人]]。他们是[[印裔巴基斯坦人|印裔巴基斯坦人]]的一部分。<ref name="Rehman2000">{{cite book|author=Javaid Rehman|title=The Weaknesses in the International Protection of Minority Rights|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HHRMEoS7-YQC&pg=PA215|date=13 April 2000|publisher=Martinus Nijhoff Publishers|isbn=90-411-1350-9|pages=215–}}</ref>

